title: SZA - Z (2014)
description:
SZA - Z

-------------------------------------------------------

SZA's first EP with TDE, the label famous for kickstarting rappers such as Kendrick Lamar and ScHoolboy Q. Super chill and very listenable, SZA's smooth voice and ear for melody along with the excellent production TDE so consistently puts out make this an extremely solid label debut.

01 - Ur
02 - Childs Play (feat. Chance the Rapper)
03 - Julia
04 - Warm Winds (feat. Isaiah Rashad)
05 - HiiiJack
06 - Green Mile
07 - Babylon (feat. Kendrick Lamar)
08 - Sweet November
09 - Shattered Ring
10 - Omega

Enjoy, and please seed!
